{
  "texts": [
    "With different functionalities, LLM agents execute in various environments, i.e., scenarios such as the Linux terminal for programming agents.",
    "LLM agents may produce safety issues in one specific scenario.",
    "To organize data in good order, we define 5 common categories of agent scenarios, including program, internet of things (IoT), software, web, and finance.",
    "Each category contains corresponding scenarios.",
    "For instance, the category of IoT comprises scenarios of smart home and traffic control."
  ]
}